âœ… 3. Use NAT Gateway for Private EC2 Internet Access

    Instances in private subnet can't access the internet directly.

    Use a NAT Gateway in a public subnet â†’ gives outbound internet access (e.g., to install packages).
    
    âœ… 4. Setup VPN Access

